title: Bump jackson-databind from 2.9.9 to 2.9.10.3

title: For very complex expressions, stack overflow
body:
Example file : 
/eclipse.jdt.core/org.eclipse.jdt.core.tests.model/workspace/Formatter/test625/A_in.java
It contains 26587 expressions.  Even we put -Xss to 4m, the file could be parsed, but the expression resolve still took very long time.

title: NullPointerException when analyzing a project
body:

How to reproduce:

```
git clone https://github.com/MariaDB/server.git
./depends.sh --auto-include -f=dot cpp /path/to/mariadb foo.bar
```
